## Project Rules
Conventions specific to this codebase.

- All editing mutations go through UndoStack::apply() — never mutate Document directly
- Offsets are UTF-8 byte offsets in Document::to_markdown() output
- MCP mode: stdout is JSON-RPC only, all logging to stderr
- GUI mode: Slint render notifier for Skia canvas, never render text in Slint components
- layout() is expensive — call only on width change or text mutation, not on repaint
- updateForegroundPaint() for hover/selection color changes without layout() cost
- Placeholder indices are position-based — keep synchronized with MediaManager
- slint-ui-templates provides shell, theme, tokens — do not duplicate in this project
- No unwrap() in production code — use ? or explicit error handling
- All pub items must have /// doc comments

